b'Kj\xc3\xa6r: \xe2\x80\x9cI have been given two years and that is the biggest signal the club can give me, that they are happy with what I have achieved so far. Like I said before, I could not be at a better place. There is no place I would rather be.\xe2\x80\x9d'

b"Kj\xc3\xa6r: \xe2\x80\x9cMy extension? Yes, of course it tells a little about my status in the club. It's a pat on the back to me because the club have a policy that they do not extend by more than one year at a time when a player is 30 years old.\xe2\x80\x9d"

b'Kj\xc3\xa6r: \xe2\x80\x9cI live in Milan, where my children are well. My wife is fine. I have talked about culture many times, and it appeals to me insanely. It is basically a combination of everything.\xe2\x80\x9d'

b'Kj\xc3\xa6r: \xe2\x80\x9cWhy is Milan the best place for me? It\xe2\x80\x99s due to the role I have in the squad, the relationship with the coach and the way we play, which is a bit reminiscent of the way we do it here on the national team.\xe2\x80\x9d'

b"Kj\xc3\xa6r: \xe2\x80\x9cHowever, when I look at my career with the places I've been, the experiences I've had, both on and off the pitch, and when I've so far been able to finish with Milan for five years. I could never have written it better myself.\xe2\x80\x9d"
